49:37.393 --> 49:41.630
Your dad-your dad was one
of the best cops I ever knew.

49:41.664 --> 49:44.132
Yeah, he was.
Don't tell Gil that.

49:44.166 --> 49:45.166
[chuckles]

49:47.469 --> 49:50.505
