why haven't you called me?

50:44.594 --> 50:46.661
I'm fine, I just stopped here
to clear my mind.

50:48.631 --> 50:50.799
Okay, I just wanted to know
you were okay.

50:53.002 --> 50:56.471
I've been worried sick.
What are you guys up to?

50:57.607 --> 51:01.009
Uh, I-I just, um, I'm baking
cookies and Heather's,

51:01.043 --> 51:05.279
uh, wrapping presents.
Um, are you at Harry's alone?

51:05.314 --> 51:08.516
