on your way, okay?

51:41.917 --> 51:43.351
[sighs]

51:50.526 --> 51:52.293
Come on, guys,
leave him alone, huh?

51:54.396 --> 51:58.166
Gentlemen,
to our fallen friends.

51:58.200 --> 52:00.368
Here, here.
To Norris and Walker.

52:03.639 --> 52:05.106
What's the matter, Duff?

52:05.141 --> 52:08.076
Too good to toast
for our friends?

52:08.110 --> 52:12.446
[Jeremy] I was there.
- Oh, yeah, right.

52:12.481 --> 52:14.082
We know you were there.

52:15.051 --> 52:16.551
[whispers]
And where were you ten years ago

52:16.585 --> 52:18.186
for the rest of them?

52:18.220 --> 52:21.089
Enough!
Seriously, guys.

52:21.123 --> 52:23.024
I've got customers in here,
okay?

52:23.059 --> 52:25.860
You think I give a shit
about customers, Harry?

52:25.895 --> 52:27.762
You know what I care about
right now?

52:27.797 --> 52:31.166
Four dead cops, Harry.
Four good cops.

52:31.200 --> 52:34.969
And for what?
Mr. Hunch over here.

52:35.004 --> 52:37.638
[laughs] Woo!

52:40.976 --> 52:42.777
And what are you telling him,
Harry?

52:42.812 --> 52:45.680
Mr. Washed Up Fucking Beat Cop?
Huh?

52:47.750 --> 52:48.837
But you know what I do know?

52:48.851 --> 52:50.785
Is you've got a pretty wife.

52:52.822 --> 52:55.690
Maybe you and I should just--
I don't know, Harry.

52:57.059 --> 53:00.428
But I've got to take a piss.
[patron] Harry, kitchen.

53:03.999 --> 53:08.669
Get the fire and...
What's going on back here?

53:13.275 --> 53:14.642
I think dad will really like it.

53:14.676 --> 53:16.945
Oh, I think he'll love it.
You did great, honey.

53:20.282 --> 53:23.551
[ominous ambience]

53:31.227 --> 53:32.593
Uh, hi, can I help you?

53:32.628 --> 53:35.830
Hi, um, sorry to bother you
