53:40.836 --> 53:43.537
Uh, friends of your father, hon.

53:43.572 --> 53:45.573
You said you had something
for him?

53:45.607 --> 53:46.674
Yeah.

53:50.379 --> 53:53.581
[whimpers]
I'm sorry it's not wrapped.

54:00.790 --> 54:04.092
Get that bitch. Hey.

54:08.363 --> 54:11.232
[whistles]

54:14.403 --> 54:16.570
[goth-rock music ♪]

54:17.639 --> 54:19.274
[Rebecca]
What do you want?

54:21.243 --> 54:22.243
You know who I am?

54:32.754 --> 54:35.523
