A real piece of shit.
You know what he said?

55:13.395 --> 55:14.562
You know what he said?

55:17.233 --> 55:18.799
He said I raped a little girl.

55:19.701 --> 55:21.802
I mean, he's right,
I did, but still.

55:21.837 --> 55:23.271
You son of a bitch.

55:23.305 --> 55:26.007
[crying]

55:26.041 --> 55:27.108
Be careful, Ms. Duffin.

55:28.210 --> 55:33.614
Be careful, or Santa ain't
